rophet laid down and turned his face to the other side. Then, Abu Bakr came in and spoke to me harshly, saying, \u201cMusical\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/30\/umar-learns-to-love-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":14245,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Umar learns to love the Prophet more","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Hisham reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he was holding the hand of Umar ibn al-Khattab. Umar said to him, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, you are more beloved to me than everything but myself.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNo, by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34057,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/03\/22\/prophet-accepts-humble-gifts\/","url_meta":{"origin":14245,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Courtesy: The Prophet accepts humble gifts and invitations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf I were invited to a meal of a simple sheep\u2019s hoof or shoulder, I would answer it. If I were given a gift of a simple sheep\u2019s hoof or shoulder, I would accept it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","